Prerequisites:
	* Visual studio 2010 (to build in windows)
	* Gcc 2.96 (to build in linux)

The project is configured to have a "vc" folder in the same level as thde solution 
folder (with the folders dll, include, and lib) with the dependencies.

Dependencies:
	* Boost Test Library
	* libxml2  library



Building using itself:
	./vsmake vsmake.sln

Building using make:
	make
	make install


More info:
	docs/building.html

